## Priorities
- Rewrite architecture to support coroutines + databindings
- Implement RoomDB and a repository for offline caching
- Hook up dependency injection
- Replace single activity with NavHostFragment

## New User Features
- Local caching of articles 
- Articles can be favourited
- Articles can be filtered to show only favourites

## New Tech 
- RoomDB
- Dagger Hilt
- Navigation component
- Databindings
- Coroutines
- Safe Args
- ListAdapter

